CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Celcuity Inc is clinical-stage biotechnology company seeking to extend the lives of cancer patients by pursuing an integrated therapeutic (Rx) and companion diagnostic (CDx) strategy. The company's drug candidate, gedatolisib, is a potent, well-tolerated, small molecule dual inhibitor, administered intravenously, that selectively targets all class I isoforms of PI3K and mammalian target of rapamycin (mTOR).
